Privacy Policy
Last Updated:
8.1.2023
This Privacy Policy explains how
AI Translator
("we," "us," or "our") collects, uses, discloses, and
                protects personal information when you use our translation service and associated mobile application
                (the "App"). By using the App, you agree to the terms outlined in this Privacy Policy.
Information We Collect
1.1 Personal Information:
We may collect certain personally identifiable information
                ("Personal Information") from you when you use our App. This may include:

User
Name

Email address

User-generated content (translations, text inputs)

Usage data (such as IP address, device information,
                operating system, and app version)

Language preferences
1.2 Non-Personal Information:
We may also collect non-personally identifiable
                information ("Non-Personal Information") that does not directly identify you. This includes aggregated
                data, statistical information, and analytical data about App usage.
How We Use Your Information
2.1 Personal
Information:
We may use your Personal Information for the following
                purposes:
To provide and improve our translation services
To communicate with you, respond to your inquiries, and
                provide customer support
To send you updates, newsletters, and promotional
                materials (with your consent)
To enforce our Terms of Service and other legal
                agreements
To protect the rights, property, or safety of
AI Translator
, our users, or others, as required or permitted by
                law
2.2 Non-Personal Information:
We may use Non-Personal Information for statistical
                analysis, research, and improving our services. This data helps us understand user preferences, usage
                patterns, and trends.
Data Sharing and Disclosure
3.1 Service Providers:
We may share your Personal Information with trusted
                third-party service providers to facilitate the functioning of our App, such as hosting, data analysis,
                and customer support. These service providers are bound by confidentiality obligations and are not
                permitted to use your information for any other purpose.
3.2 Legal Requirements:
We may disclose your Personal Information if required by
                law, court order, or governmental regulation, or if we believe it is necessary to protect our rights,
                property, or safety, or the rights, property, or safety of others.
Data Security
We take reasonable measures to protect the security of
                your Personal Information. However, please note that no method of transmission over the internet or
                electronic storage is completely secure, and we cannot guarantee absolute security.
Children's Privacy
Our App is not intended for use by children under the age
                of 13. We do not knowingly collect Personal Information from children under the age of 13. If you
                believe we have inadvertently collected such information, please contact us, and we will take steps to
                delete it.
Changes to this Privacy Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We
                will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on our website or through the App. We
                encourage you to review this Privacy Policy periodically for any changes.
Contact Us
